==English==

===Etymology===
From the Latin ''[[sonorus]]'' "resounding," from ''[[sonor]]'' "sound," from ''[[sonare]]'' "to sound"

===Adjective===
'''sonorous'''
# [[full]] of [[sound]] or [[loud]]
# [[producing]] sound (as when [[struck]])
# [[effectual]] or [[impressive]] [[speaking]] [[style]]

